urchasers\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1263}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But due to their age and condition, she said individually excavating the bricks is not possible without damaging them, and would also come with a significant cost and delay to the project schedule.\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1462, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their age\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1285}, {\"ngram\": \"condition\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1299}, {\"ngram\": \"the bricks\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1344}, {\"ngram\": \"a significant cost\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1427}, {\"ngram\": \"the project schedule\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1461}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your weekday lunchtime roundup of curated links, news highlights, analysis and features.\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1552, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your weekday lunchtime roundup\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1494}, {\"ngram\": \"curated links\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1511}, {\"ngram\": \"news highlights\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1528}, {\"ngram\": \"analysis\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1538}, {\"ngram\": \"features\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1551}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By signing up you consent to receive the above newsletter from Postmedia Network Inc. A welcome email is on its way.\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1671, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1617, \"end\": 1639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Postmedia_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Postmedia Network Inc.\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Postmedia_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Postmedia_Network\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the above newsletter\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1611}, {\"ngram\": \"A welcome email\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1655}, {\"ngram\": \"its way\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1669}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you do not see it, please check your junk folder.\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1724, \"entities\": [], 