\": \"quite an exercise\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The estimated 33,000 bricks are inscribed with the names of citizens who purchased them in 1987 for$19.88 each as a way to support Calgary hosting the 1988 Winter Olympics.\", \"from\": 2245, \"to\": 2417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2376, \"end\": 2383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Calgary\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.547771571351809e-17, \"text\": \"Calgary\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Calgary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Calgary\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The estimated 33,000 bricks\", \"from\": 2245, \"to\": 2272}, {\"ngram\": \"the names\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2301}, {\"ngram\": \"citizens\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2313}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2364}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1988 Winter Olympics\", \"from\": 2392, \"to\": 2416}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While they have been a mainstay in the plaza for nearly 40 years, the fate of the bricks hasbeen in question since 2016,when the city first engaged the public on plans to revitalize Olympic Plaza - a public space that Thompson has likened to being downtown's living room.\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2690, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2637, \"end\": 2645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.9977495241859923, \"rank\": 0.0022554074047485113, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a mainstay\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2450}, {\"ngram\": \"the plaza\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2463}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly 40 years\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2483}, {\"ngram\": \"the fate\", \"from\": 2485, \"to\": 2493}, {\"ngram\": \"the bricks\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2507}, {\"ngram\": \"question\", \"from\": 2519, \"to\": 2527}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 2544, \"to\": 2552}, {\"ngram\": \"the public\", \"from\": 2567, \"to\": 2577}, {\"ngram\": \"plans\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2586}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic Plaza\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2614}, {\"ngram\": \"a public space\", \"from\": 2617, \"to\": 2631}, {\"ngram\": \"downtown's living room\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2689}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As an alternative way to honour the bricks' legacy, she said Calgarians are invited to six events dubbed Brick by Brick throughout September.\", \"from\": 2692, \"to\": 2833, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an alternative way\", \"from\": 2695, \"to\": 2713}, {\"ngram\": \"the bricks' legacy\", \"from\": 2724, \"to\": 2742}, {\"ngram\": \"Calgarians\", \"from\": 2753, \"to\": 2763}, {\"ngram\": \"six events\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2789}, {\"ngram\": \"Brick\", \"from\": 2797, \"to\": 2802}, {\"ngram\": \"Brick\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 2811}, {\"ngram\": \"September\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2832}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said CMLC officials will be on site to help Calgarians find their engraved brick, anda photographer will capture a commemorative photo.\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2973, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"CMLC officials\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 2857}, {\"ngram\": \"site\", \"from\": 2869, \"to\": 2873}, {\"ngram\": \"Calgarians\", \"from\": 2882, \"to\": 2892}, {\"ngram\": \"their engraved brick\", \"from\": 2898, \"to\": 2918}, {\"ngram\": \"anda photographer\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2937}, {\"ngram\": \"a commemorative photo\", \"from\": 2951, \"to\": 2972}]}, {\"sentence\": \"CMLC will also provide an opportunity for Calgarians to take home a name rubbing of their brick inscription, Thompson added.\", \"from\": 2975, \"to\": 3099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3084, \"end\": 3092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.9977495241859923, \"rank\": 0.0022554074047485113, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"CMLC\", \"from\": 2975, \"to\": 2979}, {\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 2998, \"to\": 3012}, {\"ngram\": \"Calgarians\", \"from\": 3017, \"to\": 3027}, {\"ngram\": \"a name rubbing\", \"from\": 3041, \"to\": 3055}, {\"ngram\": \"their brick inscription\", \"from\": 3059, \"to\": 3082}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thom Mahler, Calgary's director of downtown strategy, said the city recognizes the bricks hold sentimental value.\", \"from\": 3101, \"to\": 3214, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3106, \"end\": 3112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gustav_Mahler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3839663822123343e-15, \"text\": \"Mahler\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gustav_Mahler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gustav_Mahler\"}, {\"begin\": 3114, \"end\": 3121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Calgary\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.547771571351809e-17, \"text\": \"Calgary\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Calgary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Calgary\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"downtown strategy\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3153}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 3160, \"to\": 3168}, {\"ngram\": \"the bricks\", \"from\": 3180, \"to\": 3190}, {\"ngram\": \"sentimental value\", \"from\": 3196, \"to\": 3213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To memorialize them, he noted the city has created a digitalized model onmaps.calgary.ca, and has created the Olympic Brick Finder tool that Calgarians can use to see a high-resolution photo of each brick.\", \"from\": 3216, \"to\": 3421, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 3246, \"to\": 3254}, {\"ngram\": \"a digitalized model\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3286}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Brick Finder tool\", \"from\": 3322, \"to\": 3351}, {\"ngram\": \"Calgarians\", \"from\": 3357, \"to\": 3367}, {\"ngram\": \"a high-resolution photo\", \"from\": 3383, \"to\": 3406}, {\"ngram\": \"each brick\", \"from\": 3410, \"to\": 3420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is really important we recognize and honour the investment Calgarians made in these bricks,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3423, \"to\": 3528, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the investment\", \"from\": 3471, \"to\": 3485}, {\"ngram\": \"Calgarians\", \"from\": 3486, \"to\": 3496}, {\"ngram\": \"these bricks\", \"from\": 3505, \"to\": 3517}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As we have heard, it's going to be very difficult, if not impossible, to remove these bricks without them crumbling.\\\"\", \"from\": 3529, \"to\": 3647, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these bricks\", \"from\": 3610, \"to\": 3622}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Though the bricks will not be part of the new-look Olympic Plaza, officials say the design team intends to incorporate other elements of the space's history, such as the skating rink that becomes a popular hub during the winter.\", \"from\": 3649, \"to\": 3877, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bricks\", \"from\": 3656, \"to\": 3666}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 3679, \"to\": 3683}, {\"ngram\": \"the new-look Olympic Plaza\", \"from\": 3687, \"to\": 3713}, {\"ngram\": \"officials\", \"from\": 3715, \"to\": 3724}, {\"ngram\": \"the design team\", \"from\": 3729, \"to\": 3744}, {\"ngram\": \"other elements\", \"from\": 3768, \"to\": 3782}, {\"ngram\": \"the space's history\", \"from\": 3786, \"to\": 3805}, {\"ngram\": \"the skating rink\", \"from\": 3815, \"to\": 3831}, {\"ngram\": \"a popular hub\", \"from\": 3845, \"to\": 3858}, {\"ngram\": \"the winter\", \"from\": 3866, \"to\": 3876}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thompson said CMLC's months-long public engagement this year - more than 3,000 Calgarians responded to a survey - revealed that most residents want to see the rink maintained.\", \"from\": 3879, \"to\": 4054, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3879, \"end\": 3887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.9977495241859923, \"rank\": 0.0022554074047485113, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"CMLC's months-long public engagement\", \"from\": 3893, \"to\": 3929}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 3,000 Calgarians\", \"from\": 3942, \"to\": 3968}, {\"ngram\": \"a survey\", \"from\": 3982, \"to\": 3990}, {\"ngram\": \"most residents\", \"from\": 4007, \"to\": 4021}, {\"ngram\": \"the rink\", \"from\": 4034, \"to\": 4042}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Respondents also said they want ample green space, lighting and live performance possibilities incorporated into the rejuvenated plaza.\", \"from\": 4056, \"to\": 4191, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Respondents\", \"from\": 4056, \"to\": 4067}, {\"ngram\": \"ample green space\", \"from\": 4088, \"to\": 4105}, {\"ngram\": \"lighting\", \"from\": 4107, \"to\": 4115}, {\"ngram\": \"live performance possibilities\", \"from\": 4120, \"to\": 4150}, {\"ngram\": \"the rejuvenated plaza\", \"from\": 4169, \"to\": 4190}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This space is used by so many different communities and groups to celebrate,\\\" Thompson said.\", \"from\": 4193, \"to\": 4286, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4272, \"end\": 4280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.9977495241859923, \"rank\": 0.0022554074047485113, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This space\", \"from\": 4194, \"to\": 4204}, {\"ngram\": \"so many different communities\", \"from\": 4216, \"to\": 4245}, {\"ngram\": \"groups\", \"from\": 4250, \"to\": 4256}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We want to make that as easy as possible and as adaptable as possible, so people can come down here, host a festival, have a great concert and also just come down on Saturday to have a coffee and gather.\\\"\", \"from\": 4287, \"to\": 4492, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 4362, \"to\": 4368}, {\"ngram\": \"a festival\", \"from\": 4394, \"to\": 4404}, {\"ngram\": \"a great concert\", \"from\": 4411, \"to\": 4426}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 4454, \"to\": 4462}, {\"ngram\": \"a coffee\", \"from\": 4471, \"to\": 4479}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The reimagination of Olympic Plaza is part of a larger $660-million transformation of Arts Commons, which includes a new concert venue on the west side.\", \"from\": 4494, \"to\": 4646, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4580, \"end\": 4592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arts_Commons\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Arts Commons\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arts_Commons\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arts_Commons\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The reimagination\", \"from\": 4494, \"to\": 4511}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic Plaza\", \"from\": 4515, \"to\": 4528}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 4532, \"to\": 4536}, {\"ngram\": \"a larger $660-million transformation\", \"from\": 4540, \"to\": 4576}, {\"ngram\": \"a new concert venue\", \"from\": 4609, \"to\": 4628}, {\"ngram\": \"the west side\", \"from\": 4632, \"to\": 4645}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In March, Premier Danielle Smith announced the provincewould contribute more than $100 milliontoward the coinciding projects, stating the rejuvenations would help breathe new life into Calgary's downtown and arts scene.\", \"from\": 4648, \"to\": 4867, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4666, \"end\